content.rendered:
Directed by Chuck Russell.

Written by Raaghav Dar. Adam Prince. Chuck Russell. Ritesh Shah. Rohan Sippy.

Cast Lars Kjeldsen(Mr. Vane) . Asha Bhat(Meera). Vishwanath Chatterjee(Khan). Kumkum Das(Mrs. Pasha). Makrand Deshpande(Gaja Guru). Gaurav Dewasi(Friend). Rohan Joshi(Jayesh). Vicky Kadian(Vicky Kadian). Atul Kulkarni(Keshav). Shivani Mahajan(Nandini). Ratnesh Mani(Ranger). Akshay Oberoi(Dev).Dinesh Rajpurohit.Rahul Verma Rajput. Madhurima Roy(Michelle). Pooja Sawant(Shankara). Abhijit Sinha(Cop). Thalaivasal Vijay(Dipankar Nair).Vishwanath.Shankar Yadav. Ania Zeyne(Crimson Lady) . (0)

Language Hindi.

Producers Vishesh Agrawal. Vineet Jain. Hetvi Karia. Uzma Khan. Yogendra Mogre. Priti Shahani. Dharam Soni. Yogesh Tevatia. Shilpan Vyas Tinu. Vicky Vijay. Ania Zeyne.

Production Junglee Pictures.
